 《侍僧》明星朱迪·特纳-史密斯批评迪士尼没有保护演员免受种族主义强烈抵制https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-acolyte-star-jodie-turner-smith-criticises-disney-for-not-defending-cast-from-racist-backlash-3800112?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=侍僧明星朱迪·特纳·史密斯批评迪士尼不为种族主义者辩护演员阵容Sam WarnerMon, 07 Oct 2024 11:09:49 +0000 NewsTV NewsStar Wars https://www.nme.com/?p=3800112 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="朱迪·特纳·史密斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “什么都不说是不公平的。这真的不公平”</p><p> 《侍僧》主演朱迪·特纳-史密斯在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上首次发表文章<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-acolyte-star-jodie-turner-smith-criticises-disney-for-not-defending-cast-from-racist-backlash-3800112">，批评迪士尼没有保护演员免受种族主义强烈抵制</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="朱迪·特纳·史密斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jodie-Turner-Smith-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-acolyte"><em>《侍僧》的</em></a>主演朱迪·特纳-史密斯批评<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">迪士尼</a>在种族主义强烈反对下没有为该剧的明星辩护。</p><p> 《<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars"><em>星球大战》</em></a>系列故事背景设定在前传电影大约 100 年前，早在 6 月就在 Disney+ 上首映，不过最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-acolyte-has-reportedly-been-cancelled-at-disney-after-just-one-season-3785072">在播出一季后被取消</a>。</p><p>然而，该剧的一些明星在上映期间受到了种族歧视，阿曼德拉·斯坦伯格此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-acolyte-actor-drops-song-in-response-to-star-wars-fan-backlash-3767649">曾分享过一首歌曲来回应她所受到的虐待</a>。这位明星后来承认，该剧的取消对她来说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-acolyte-star-says-shows-cancellation-was-not-a-huge-shock-after-rampage-of-vitriol-3788534">“并不是一个巨大的震惊”</a> ，特别是在演员们受到“尖酸刻薄的攻击”之后。</p><p>特纳·史密斯饰演阿尼塞娅母亲——抚养斯坦伯格饰演的奥莎和梅的女巫团的领袖——声称迪士尼在种族主义强烈反对中保持沉默是“不公平的”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="侍僧 |官方预告片|迪士尼+" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BtytYWhg2mc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “当人们在互联网上充斥着种族主义和废话时，他们必须停止这样做，他们什么也不说，”她告诉<a href="https://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/article/jodie-turner-smith-interview-2024-glamour-women-of-the-year-awards" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《魅力》杂志</em></a>。 “什么都不说是不公平的。实在是太不公平了。</p><p> “如果有钱的人（迪士尼或其他工作室）能够表现出支持并坚定立场，那就太好了。说这是不可接受的：“如果你这样做，你就不是粉丝。”发表一个非常重要的声明，看看是否有钱离开。</p><p> “我敢打赌不会，因为有色人种，尤其是黑人，在购买力中占有很大比例。他们可能会发现这实际上对他们来说更有利可图，但每个人都在使用“唤醒”，就像它是一个肮脏的词一样。”</p><p>特纳-史密斯接着表示希望“观点改变”和“流行改变”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C8aorYEx2ZQ/?